{"tid":399161,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到個菲林相機app","createTime":"2017-09-13T17:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T20:20:43.000Z","uid":79513,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aadbc464bfa37ad9726bdfffc1d464786b5353c","tid":399161,"uid":79513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"見依家咁多人比$8買個個要等3日嘅菲林相機app，<br />\n頭先搵到個係唔洗錢嘅，並唔係咩打手係到講因係想比大家有多個好app用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011016_a52e42597f871c821d71a6e74b3715d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F011016_a52e42597f871c821d71a6e74b3715d5.jpg&h=c48879bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApp名<br />\n<br />\n以下係無聊嘅生活照<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011211_19384c35cf6d1b247006b342804d7200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F011211_19384c35cf6d1b247006b342804d7200.jpg&h=9a9f4768&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011212_fe52b42a670383f1a6113097d49f18cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F011212_fe52b42a670383f1a6113097d49f18cb.jpg&h=e7c18bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢有幾個鏡比人唔洗錢用，平時玩下我就覺得夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be4a84ce16b843920702724002997193e313bf1","tid":399161,"uid":79513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011414_cf7430eebf11f6385f6b61bcbdb55820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F011414_cf7430eebf11f6385f6b61bcbdb55820.jpg&h=262552d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011433_b4dfed4c5673a6379b1c26fd16061d37.jpg\" data-th